    "• AROMA: Training procedure follows ENMA.",
    "2D datasets are trained for 1, 000 epochs.",
    "• CORAL: To stabilize training, the KL loss term is removed.",
    "The model is trained as a standard autoencoder minimizing relative MSE, with an initial learning rate of 1e-6.",
    "• Oformer: Follows the same training procedure as ENMA."
